Package ninja.jira.skeletonkey.app.controller

Class RecurringPaymentController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ninja.jira.skeletonkey.app.controller.RecurringPaymentController
  • @CrossOrigin
@Controller
@RequestMapping(path="/api/recurringpayment")
public class RecurringPaymentController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the controller for class RecurringPayment. Payments occur daily/weekly/monthly Transactions are performed automatically on every first day For example, first day of the week, first day of the month Uses GET methods when retrieving data from db Uses POST methods otherwise
